al crisis同death anxiety<br />\n一諗起死亡就會好恐懼然後有啲呼吸困難咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1c77d82e2711e872c702d70d70a9725dc43632","tid":2462070,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:06:38.000Z","msg":"我係驚死咗身邊嘅人難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然生存真係好辛苦 <br />\n但佢地係我堅持嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b952561581901f5667397fd02ba015698504c8b7","tid":2462070,"uid":118746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:13:01.000Z","msg":"我驚呢個世界真係有鬼，死完都解脫唔到，仲要做鬼流連喺度，唔開心回憶忘記唔到，從此見到身邊人又無辦法叫佢地，如果世界真係無鬼，死完就係長眠咁就唔怕"},{"pid":"63d06f9db885a9d9e831c71912f05936ef6f4c75","tid":2462070,"uid":107217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"591c08b128851d0cecfd5b4e6d8d7750ceef4d87","tid":2462070,"uid":250887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"成日都會諗人死咗會去邊<br />\n身邊啲人會講死有咩好驚<br />\n但係死咗咩都冇 唔知會去邊 呢種恐懼真係糾纏咗我好多年<br />\n點樣先可以唔驚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:19:30.000Z","msg":"生存都味驚死點會驚，你諗下人為咗生存犧牲幾多動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaa2c4b89780893374bb1aa344af945cd241c70","tid":2462070,"uid":202125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef9d30f17ba656aa32060c9bb687eb664774f966","tid":2462070,"uid":373626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e24387f75da2ffa01babf302324ed3fcea9c4ccc","tid":2462070,"uid":231231,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"成日諗死後會唔會仲有知覺<br />\n火葬會唔會好痛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:37:39.000Z","msg":"岩啊 細個成日同我媽講我死咗要土葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:33:21.000Z","msg":"土葬黎個突然回光返照 透唔到氣仲要比蟲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993e33f2fbaabd20e77eece2292c38db8f898942","tid":2462070,"uid":306095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:51:37.000Z","msg":"會諗意識去咗邊度 會唔會思考<br />\n不過諗諗下 驚自己重病多過死"},{"pid":"5f51120bb005cad857625beb244213240456de47","tid":2462070,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"死左咩都冇, 所以冇得驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係 死既過程可能好痛苦, 呢樣先驚"},{"pid":"6de59c406dcff86bd0543b375704dcc013aa987e","tid":2462070,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:05:22.000Z","msg":"驚老同死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a770731de8ac9912e17cc5a8e5a4b273cdd2d4","tid":2462070,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc47a8172a171685a5f189fd81b0432ee314241d","tid":2462070,"uid":201833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:10:39.000Z","msg":"轉另一個角度諗，如果你自己一個可以好長命even係永生，咁你又點？ 去到7，80歳，你身邊嘅人走曬，再過多幾十年可能你啲孫都走埋，即係同你同時代嘅一批人都走曬嘅時候，你又會係點？ 就算你不停識新嘅人，佢哋都會有離開嘅一日，咁你又點。好啦，當你可以見證住時代嘅變遷，科技嘅發展，好多野都好先進嘅時候，你可以同邊個分享？ 邊個可以代入到你見證時代變遷嘅角度去睇？ 其實講到尾，活得耐只有寂寞兩隻字。不如順其自然好過，過好每一日充實自己嘅人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:06:03.000Z","msg":"大師"},{"pid":"de2d15e7631f9237157036a7e66f2bc56956095c","tid":2462070,"uid":217336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:08:03.000Z","msg":"人唔會死先恐怖<br />\n人間其實係一個地獄，你哩一刻如果叫做活得幾開心，咁恭喜你，但有一日你開始老，開始多慢性病，開始經歷得多身邊人嘅生老病死，咁死都算係一種解脫"},{"pid":"8ca7afc6c1cade6bc64572e56219023e3fd83094","tid":2462070,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:08:34.000Z","msg":"如果投胎由三國時代開始排隊，有排排啊，成百幾億人<br />\n<br />\n應該好似訓覺無知覺但你唔會起身"},{"pid":"e6fb7f954a8