sg":"有 但係都係好驚"},{"pid":"1c19593e3de2da78863c5f3187e047d7cac623c4","tid":2462070,"uid":250887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b8a2ebbdc0586c71947313ba94c546015e6da6b","tid":2462070,"uid":335664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:16:57.000Z","msg":"推薦你睇靈魂奇遇記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"我睇咗<br />\n但係我唔知點樣先叫珍惜當下<br />\n咩先係珍惜當下好好活著<br />\n咩叫做唔想死咗發生自己一生毫無意義<br />\n成日話個意義係自己俾 點樣俾..<br />\n好迷惘"},{"pid":"55a89374bde03d31738a1940735e327a463dc300","tid":2462070,"uid":212771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"死唔唔係解脫咩,終於唔洗生存係呢個痴撚線世界"},{"pid":"b51a5117ed9ad34083033d071589fc213d46e7e7","tid":2462070,"uid":53530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:50:31.000Z","msg":"最驚係死左帶唔走D錢 依家咁努力搵完既錢 之後帶唔走 諗起就好驚"}]}